        "y": 750
      },
      "data": {
        "schemaType": "msgbox",
        "text": "QUIN: -- and THAT is our new\nneighbor’s house! Rating: four\nout of ten. Could use landscaping.\n\nOh! You’re the new kid! I’m QUIN!\n\nI’m documenting my entire POKeMON\njourney for my followers.\nI have seven followers.\nSix of them are my mom on alt\naccounts.",
        "msgType": "MSGBOX_DEFAULT"
      },
      "measured": {
        "width": 240,
        "height": 74
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "node-37",
      "type": "script",
      "position": {
        "x": 705.7142857142858,
        "y": 900
      },
      "data": {
        "schemaType": "msgbox",
        "text": "QUIN: You’re going on a journey\ntoo, right? RIGHT?\n\nPlease say yes. I need a rival\nfor content. Solo journeys don’t\nget engagement.",
        "msgType": "MSGBOX_DEFAULT"
      },
      "measured": {
        "width": 240,
        "height": 74
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "node-38",
      "type": "script",
      "position": {
        "x": 705.7142857142858,
        "y": 1050
      },
      "data": {
        "schemaType": "msgbox",
        "text": "QUIN: So you’ll be my rival?",
        "msgType": "MSGBOX_YESNO"
      },
      "measured": {
        "width": 240,
        "height": 74
      }
    },
